    The default Look and Feel, when no look and feel is selected, or the selected one can not be found, this package is used.
    The look and feel packages need to contain a InitInterface class named Init, a FormLAF and a class LAF per each FormControl in the org.universAAL.ui.handler.gui.swing.classic.handler.gui.swing.model.FormControl package.

    The default Look and Feel, when no look and feel is selected, or the selected one can not be found, this package is used.
